### 所有请求都带上uid参数,并且header中带上 Authorization:token
@url = http://localhost:8895

### 1️⃣ 新增频道
POST {{url}}/app/channel/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uid": 1,
  "account_name": "testuser@gmail.com",
  "channel_name": "Test Channel"
}

### 2️⃣ 获取频道详情
GET {{url}}/app/channel/get?channel_id=1

