### 3️⃣ 更新频道信息
PUT {{url}}/app/channel/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel_id": 1,
  "channel_name": "Updated Channel Name",
  "is_synced_today": "yes"
}

### 4️⃣ 删除频道
DELETE {{url}}/app/channel/delete?channel_id=1

### 5️⃣ 获取频道列表（分页）
GET {{url}}/app/channel/list?page=1&size=10&uid=1

